edu.umass.cs.reconfiguration.reconfigurationprotocoltasks

Class CommitWorker<NodeIDType>

  • java.lang.Object
    • edu.umass.cs.reconfiguration.reconfigurationprotocoltasks.CommitWorker<NodeIDType>
  • Type Parameters:
    NodeIDType - This class is not a protocol task, just a usual runnable worker. It is initiated at a reconfigurator in order to commit the coordinated RCRecordRequest packets. We need a task for this because simply invoking handleIncoming (that in turn calls paxos propose) does not suffice to ensure that the command will be eventually committed.
    All Implemented Interfaces:
    java.lang.Runnable
